 most DKPs earned (this figure includes level incentive DKPs) will receive the drop. If there is a tie in DKPs earned, the players will random for the drop.<br><br>- Epic drops from raids which must be scheduled by the epic coordinator (raids which require more than one group) will cost the player receiving the drop 0.5 DKPs for each drop. The more 2+ group raids an epic requires the more the epic will cost in terms of DKPs. This, however, is not a prohibitive cost, but it does give players a sense and responsibility as to the guild's resource commitment for their epic. This is also fair to those members who join the guild with a portion of their epic completed. All in all, one DKP per 2+ group epic drop should not be an amount that would keep a player from completing their epic. <br><br>- Effective October 15, 2001, no epic encounters will be scheduled by the epic coordinator for persons whose total earned DKPs are less than 20.<br> <p>Slaas<br>Warlord of <a href="http://www.sacrosanctguild.com/"> Sacrosanct </a><br>Ombudsman</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub46.ezboard.com/fdivinity14264frm4.showNextMessage?topicID=9.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub46.ezboard.com/fdivinity14264frm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9.topic><img src=http://www.sacrosanctguild.com/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub46.ezboard.com/fdivinity14264frm4.threadControl?topicID=9.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub46.ezboard.com/fdivinity14264frm4.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=9.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub46.ezboard.com/fdivinity14264